# Navigation

**Figma:** [Navigation](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=516-12822&p=f&m=dev)

Structure, tabs, nav list, and token mappings below are derived from Figma node 516:12822.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Top bar bg (default) | `--bg-base-default` |
| Top bar bg (dark) | `--bg-base-secondary` |
| Logo/accents | `--text-brand-default` |
| Text/icons | `--text-base-default` |
| Tab default | `--bg-base-default`, `--border-base-default` |
| Tab active | `--border-brand-default` underline |
| Tab hover | `--bg-base-tertiary` |
| Tab selected | `--bg-brand-default`, `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Nav item default | `--bg-base-default`, `--text-base-default` |
| Nav item selected | `--bg-brand-tertiary`, `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Chevron default | `--text-base-secondary` |

---

## Structure

### Top bar (NavBar)
- **Height:** ~64px; Space/800 padding.
- **Layout:** Logo left; nav items center/right; search + CTA right.
- **Background:** `--bg-base-default` or `--bg-base-secondary` (dark variant).

### Tab / Title elements
- **Context:** On Base/Default (white) or Base/Secondary (grey) background.

### Navigation list items
- **Structure:** Checkbox (left) + "Navigation Title" + Chevron (right).
- **SECTION headers:** Uppercase; group items hierarchically.

---

## Tab states

| State | On Base/Default | On Base/Secondary |
|-------|----------------|-------------------|
| Default | `--bg-base-default` bg, `--border-base-default` border; `--text-base-default` | Same; adapted for `--bg-base-secondary` |
| Active | `--border-brand-default` underline; `--text-base-default` | Same |
| Hover | `--bg-base-tertiary` fill + `--border-brand-default` underline | Same |
| Selected | `--bg-brand-default` bg, `--text-brand-on-brand` | Same |

---

## Nav list states

| State | Background | Text | Checkbox | Chevron |
|-------|------------|------|----------|---------|
| Default | `--bg-base-default` | `--text-base-default` | Empty | `--text-base-secondary` |
| Selected | `--bg-brand-tertiary` | `--text-brand-on-brand` | Filled | Matching |
| Focused | Same | Bold | Empty or filled | `--border-brand-default` outline |

---

## Spacing

- Space/200–300 between items.
- Space/400 before SECTION header.
- Space/400–600 between nav items in top bar.

---

## Icons

- **Checkbox:** Square; empty (default) or filled (selected).
- **Chevron:** Right-pointing; `--text-base-secondary` (default) or `--text-brand-on-brand` (selected).

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Mobile: Hamburger menu; drawer/overlay.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 516:12822.
